WEBVTT

00:01:29.160 --> 00:01:32.336
where aspirations
are linked to opportunity

00:01:32.360 --> 00:01:35.096
and you get dynamism and economic growth,

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:38.856
like that which happened
in the country I was born in, in Korea?

00:01:38.880 --> 00:01:43.120
Or are aspirations
going to meet frustration?

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:47.600
This is a real concern,
because between 2012 and 2015,

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:51.336
terrorism incidents
increased by 74 percent.

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:55.616
The number of deaths from terrorism
went up 150 percent.

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:57.496
Right now, two billion people

00:01:57.520 --> 00:02:00.096
live in conditions
of fragility, conflict, violence,